  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/948900/extras/6e751a0ce4d7b5c24388d62c111656a9.poster.avif?t=1641673511\" ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/948900/extras/6e751a0ce4d7b5c24388d62c111656a9.webm?t=1641673511\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >what awaits you in this game;</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>puzzles<br></li><li>more puzzles<br></li><li>good jokes (also some bad jokes)<br></li><li>AI & and a robot<br></li><li>dark humour<br></li><li>much more puzzles <br></li><li>parody and satire (still I don't know the difference between them) <br></li><li>single eyes<br></li><li>riddles & hidden messages</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >what you need to do in this game;</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/948900/extras/eb1a8c07d526a712f6d2ff5190f9f717.poster.avif?t=1641673511\" width=614 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/948900/extras/eb1a8c07d526a712f6d2ff5190f9f717.webm?t=1641673511\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/948900/extras/eb1a8c07d526a712f6d2ff5190f9f717.mp4?t=1641673511\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>just solve the puzzles, <i>if you can</i><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >what you should bring with you while playing this game;</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>a keyboard <br></li><li>a mouse<br></li><li>a working brain (preferably the human brain)</li></ul>",
